text_raw:
1. These Regulations may be cited as the Avian Influenza (Biosecurity 
Measures) Regulations 2022 (Revocation) Regulations 2023 and come into 
operation on 2 June 2023.

text_raw:
2. The Avian Influenza (Biosecurity Measures) Regulations 2022 are 

revoked. 

GIVEN under my Official Seal, 

1 June, 2023. 

CHARLIE MCCONALOGUE, 

Minister for Agriculture, Food and the Marine. 

Notice of the making of this Statutory Instrument was published in 
"Iris Oifigiúil" of 2nd June, 2023.
